不改变分式的值，使下列分式的分子和分母都不含“一”号：

(1) $\frac{-5y}{-x^2}$ ;

(2) $\frac{-a}{2b}$ ;

(3) $\frac{4m}{-3n}$ ;

（4） $-\frac{-x}{2y}$

计算：

(1) $\frac{3a}{4b} \cdot \frac{16b}{9a^2}$ ;   
(2) $\frac{12xy}{5a} \div 8x^2y$ ;   
(3) $(-3xy) \div \frac{2y^2}{3x}$ ;   
(4) $\frac{x + y}{x - y} \cdot \frac{y - x}{x + y}$ .

计算：

(1) $\frac{2m^2n}{3pq^2} \cdot \frac{5p^2q}{4mn^2} \div \frac{5mnp}{3q}$ ;

(2) $\frac{16 - a^2}{a^2 + 8a + 16} \div \frac{a - 4}{2a + 8} \cdot \frac{a - 2}{a + 2}$ .

计算：

(1) $\left(\frac{-2x^4y^2}{3z}\right)^3$ ;

(2) $\left(\frac{2ab^3}{-c^2d}\right)^2 \div \frac{6a^4}{b^3} \cdot \left(\frac{-3c}{b^2}\right)^3$ .

计算：

(1) $\frac{1}{2c^2d} + \frac{1}{3cd^2}$ ;

(2) $\frac{3}{2m - n} - \frac{2m - n}{(2m - n)^2}$ ;

(3) $\frac{a}{a^2 - b^2} - \frac{1}{a + b}$ ;

(4) $\frac{a^2}{a - 1} - a - 1$ .

例7 计算 $\left(\frac{2a}{b}\right)^2 \cdot \frac{1}{a - b} - \frac{a}{b} \div \frac{b}{4}$ .

解： $\left(\frac{2a}{b}\right)^2\cdot \frac{1}{a - b} -\frac{a}{b}\div \frac{b}{4}$

$$
\begin{array}{l} = \frac {4 a ^ {2}}{b ^ {2}} \cdot \frac {1}{a - b} - \frac {a}{b} \cdot \frac {4}{b} \\ = \frac {4 a ^ {2}}{b ^ {2} (a - b)} - \frac {4 a}{b ^ {2}} = \frac {4 a ^ {2}}{b ^ {2} (a - b)} - \frac {4 a (a - b)}{b ^ {2} (a - b)} \\ = \frac {4 a ^ {2} - 4 a ^ {2} + 4 a b}{b ^ {2} (a - b)} = \frac {4 a b}{b ^ {2} (a - b)} \\ = \frac {4 a}{a b - b ^ {2}}. \\ \end{array}
$$

式与数有相同的混合运算顺序：先乘方，再乘除，然后加减.

例8 计算：

(1) $\left(m + 2 + \frac{5}{2 - m}\right) \cdot \frac{2m - 4}{3 - m}$ ;

(2) $\left(\frac{x + 2}{x^2 - 2x} - \frac{x - 1}{x^2 - 4x + 4}\right) \div \frac{x - 4}{x}$ .

解：(1) $\left(m + 2 + \frac{5}{2 - m}\right) \cdot \frac{2m - 4}{3 - m}$

$$
\begin{array}{l} = \frac {(m + 2) (2 - m) + 5}{2 - m} \cdot \frac {2 m - 4}{3 - m} \\ = \frac {9 - m ^ {2}}{2 - m} \cdot \frac {2 (m - 2)}{3 - m} \\ = \frac {(3 - m) (3 + m)}{2 - m} \cdot \frac {- 2 (2 - m)}{3 - m} \\ = - 2 (m + 3) = - 2 m - 6; \\ \end{array}
$$

(2) $\left(\frac{x + 2}{x^2 - 2x} - \frac{x - 1}{x^2 - 4x + 4}\right) \div \frac{x - 4}{x}$

$$
\begin{array}{l} = \left[ \frac {x + 2}{x (x - 2)} - \frac {x - 1}{(x - 2) ^ {2}} \right] \cdot \frac {x}{x - 4} \\ = \frac {(x + 2) (x - 2) - (x - 1) x}{x (x - 2) ^ {2}} \cdot \frac {x}{x - 4} \\ = \frac {x ^ {2} - 4 - x ^ {2} + x}{(x - 2) ^ {2} (x - 4)} \\ = \frac {1}{(x - 2) ^ {2}}. \\ \end{array}
$$

